name: Experiment Or Die #93
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays design is me thinking out loud on how I can evolve this collection and continue to add fun and added value as we go along. I imagine the Alphabyte is an open edition or one with a large edition number that you can use to pair with any 1 of 1 and turn it into a playable letter piece. I like that idea. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
